---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Responsible Investment | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
  description="Tierra Viva approaches responsibility through governance, environmental resilience, social foundations, and stewardship."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">
      Responsible Investment as a Source of Resilience
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-forest-dark/95">
      For Tierra Viva, responsible investment is not a separate objectiveâ€”it
      is integral to how long-term value is protected and compounded.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-forest-dark/95">
      We approach responsibility through a pragmatic, governance-led lens,
      focusing on the factors most material to durable real-asset performance
      in emerging markets.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-forest-dark/95">
      Our approach emphasizes:
    </p>
    <ul
      class="mt-6 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-forest-dark/95"
      role="list"
    >
      <li>
        <strong>Governance &amp; Transparency:</strong> Clear oversight
        structures, disciplined capital allocation, and transparent reporting
        aligned with international best practices.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Environmental Resilience:</strong> Infrastructure, energy, and
        water systems designed to reduce operating risk, enhance efficiency,
        and support long-term asset durability.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Social Foundations:</strong> Education access, local employment
        pathways, and community integration that strengthen demand stability
        and long-term occupancy.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Stewardship Orientation:</strong> Development decisions
        evaluated not only on near-term returns, but on their ability to
        sustain value across economic cycles.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-tierra-forest-dark/95">
      We intend to report on selected, material indicators over time as
      projects advance, with a focus on substance over signaling.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-10">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="font-medium text-tierra-forest underline decoration-tierra-mid underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-tierra-forest focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-tierra-lime focus:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Back to home
      </a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
